        <div class=3D"article-headline">
           =20
               =20
                <h1 id=3D"id_title">The Most Batsh*t Insane Moments in The =
Wolfenstein Series</h1>
               =20
           =20
           =20
        </div>
        <div class=3D"article-sub-headline">
            <h3 id=3D"id_deck">Spoilers aHead.</h3>
        </div>

       =20
       =20
            <div class=3D"affiliation-disclaimer">This post might contain a=
ffiliation links. If you buy something through this post, the publisher may=
 get a share of the sale.</div>
       =20
        <div class=3D"article-byline">
            <section class=3D"article-authors">
                <div class=3D"author-byline-images"><a href=3D"https://sea.=
ign.com/u/ign-staff"><img class=3D"roundendimg" src=3D"https://oystatic.ign=
imgs.com/src/core/img/social/avatars/ign.jpg" alt=3D"Ign Staff"></a></div><=
div class=3D"author-names"><span class=3D"byname">By</span>&nbsp;<span clas=
s=3D"reviewer hcard"><a class=3D"url" href=3D"https://sea.ign.com/u/ign-sta=
ff">Ign Staff</a></span>&nbsp;</div>
            </section>
            <div class=3D"divider"></div>
           =20
            <div class=3D"article-publish-date">
                <span>Updated: July 27, 2019, 6:46 a.m.</span>
            </div>
           =20
        </div>

        <section class=3D"side-by-side article-content">
            <article class=3D"article-section article-page">
               =20
                <div id=3D"id_text" itemprop=3D"articleBody">
                   =20
                        <div class=3D"recirc-title pos0"><span>Related read=
s:</span><a href=3D"https://sea.ign.com/maplestorysea/228113/news/maplestor=
ysea-celebrates-20th-anniversary-with-massive-summer-updates" class=3D"reci=
rc_odd"><span>MapleStorySEA Celebrates 20th Anniversary With Massive Summer=
 Updates</span><svg class=3D"icon-top-right-arrow" focusable=3D"false" view=
Box=3D"0 0 32 32" aria-hidden=3D"true" role=3D"presentation" stroke-width=
=3D"2"><path fill=3D"none" stroke=3D"currentColor" stroke-linecap=3D"round"=
 stroke-linejoin=3D"round" d=3D"m19.961 5.397 10.04 10.039-10.04 10.038M2.3=
94 15.436h26.351" transform=3D"rotate(-45, 16, 16)"></path></svg></a></div>
                       =20
                        <p dir=3D"ltr">Now that Wolfenstein: Youngblood is =
out in the wild, we decided it would be a good time to round up the most ba=
tsh*t insane moments in MachineGames=E2=80=99 Wolfenstein series so far, wh=
ich was a hard task considering the series is known for being, well, batsh*=
t insane in general.
<strong>Spoilers ahead.&nbsp;</strong></p><p></p><div class=3D"mobileArticl=
eAds mrec1"><div class=3D"zad halfpage" data-zadtype=3D"halfpage" data-suff=
ix=3D"mrec1"></div></div><aside class=3D"floatrecirc onlymobile"><span clas=
s=3D"recirc-title">More like this</span><a href=3D"https://sea.ign.com/amaz=
on-deals/219946/deal/open-back-headphones-a-sound-experience-like-no-other"=
 class=3D"recirc_odd"><img class=3D"image" src=3D"https://sm.ign.com/t/ign_=
ap/screenshot/default/collection-of-the-main-image-for-the-articles-4_pz16.=
640.png" alt=3D"Open Back Headphones: A Sound Experience Like No Other"><sp=
an class=3D"recirctext">Open Back Headphones: A Sound Experience Like No Ot=
her<svg class=3D"icon-top-right-arrow" focusable=3D"false" viewBox=3D"0 0 3=
2 32" aria-hidden=3D"true" role=3D"presentation" stroke-width=3D"2"><path f=
ill=3D"none" stroke=3D"currentColor" stroke-linecap=3D"round" stroke-linejo=
in=3D"round" d=3D"m19.961 5.397 10.04 10.039-10.04 10.038M2.394 15.436h26.3=
51" transform=3D"rotate(-45, 16, 16)"></path></svg></span></a></aside>
<p></p><div class=3D"gallery_embed"><iframe allowautoplay=3D"" class=3D"gal=
lery" frameborder=3D"0" id=3D"gallery152124" scrolling=3D"no" src=3D"cid:fr=
ame-6CDB0017ED11FA69B6F0AC1727C258C4@mhtml.blink"></iframe></div>
<p></p><h2>Hitler=E2=80=99s Appearance in the Wolfenstein 2: The New Coloss=
us</h2>
I=E2=80=99m not sure there=E2=80=99s ever been a more repulsive character i=
n the rebooted Wolfenstein series than Hitler, which is fitting of course, =
as he was an incredibly repulsive man in real life. Nonetheless, that didn=
=E2=80=99t make his pissing, puking, murdering actions in the New Colossus =
any less disturbing.&nbsp;<em>- Lucy O'Brien</em><p></p>
<p><a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/HITLE=
R.png" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/ImageObject"><img alt=
=3D"HITLER" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2184188" height=3D"405=
" src=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/HITLER-72=
0x405.png" width=3D"720" data-position=3D"0"><link href=3D"https://oyster.i=
gnimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/HITLER-720x405.png" itemprop=3D"ur=
l"></a>
</p><div class=3D"vplayer"><iframe allow=3D"autoplay" allowautoplay=3D"" al=
lowfullscreen=3D"" class=3D"video" data-src=3D"/pc/152059/video/embed" gest=
ure=3D"media" scrolling=3D"no"></iframe></div>
<p></p><h2>B.J. Fights With His Dad While His House is Falling From the Sky=
 in Wolfenstein 2: The New Colossus</h2>
There are action set pieces, and then there is fighting a wave of robots an=
d Nazis while falling from the sky in your childhood home. One of the narra=
tives in Wolfenstein The New Colossus is how B.J. tackles this traumatic ch=
ildhood. And when he finally confronts his abusive father in his old house,=
 the developers decided to use the emotionally charged moment to stage one =
of the most intense and batshit crazy gameplay moments in the entire series=
.<em> - Matt Kim&nbsp;</em><p></p>
<p><a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/DAD.j=
pg" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/ImageObject"><img alt=3D"=
DAD" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2184189" data-src=3D"https://=
oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/DAD-720x405.jpg" height=3D=
"405" src=3D"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=3D'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'=
 viewBox=3D'0 0 16 9'%3E%3C/svg%3E" width=3D"720" data-position=3D"1"><link=
 href=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/DAD-720x4=
05.jpg" itemprop=3D"url"></a>
</p><h2>The Wheelchair Level in Wolfenstein 2: The New Colossus</h2>
MachineGames loves to tear down hero B.J. Blazkowicz any chance they get. W=
hen the events of Wolfenstein 2: The New Colossus begins, B.J. is still dea=
ling with the repercussions of his fight with Deathshead, in that he wakes =
up with a severely weakened body. When the Nazis invade the U-Boat B.J. is =
on, he has no choice but to mow them down whilst bound to a wheelchair. It=
=E2=80=99s a frantic, exhilarating opening that sets the tone for Wolfenste=
in 2=E2=80=99s increasingly crazy moments.&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>- Matt Kim</em><p=
></p>
<p><a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/WHEEL=
CHAIR.png" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/ImageObject"><img =
alt=3D"WHEELCHAIR" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2184190" data-s=
rc=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/WHEELCHAIR-7=
20x405.png" height=3D"405" src=3D"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=3D'http:/=
/www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox=3D'0 0 16 9'%3E%3C/svg%3E" width=3D"720" data=
-position=3D"2"><link href=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.=
com/2019/07/WHEELCHAIR-720x405.png" itemprop=3D"url"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p></p><div class=3D"vplayer"><iframe allow=3D"autoplay" allowautoplay=3D""=
 allowfullscreen=3D"" class=3D"video" data-src=3D"https://widgets.ign.com/v=
ideo/embed/content.html?url=3Dhttps://www.ign.com/videos/2019/07/26/wolfens=
tein-youngblood-the-movie-all-cutscenes" gesture=3D"media" scrolling=3D"no"=
></iframe></div>
<p></p><h2>Engel Gets Her Face Smashed by That Giant Robot in Wolfenstein: =
The New Order</h2>
Engel is a villain you just love to hate. That=E2=80=99s why it feels so go=
od to see her get decked by a giant robot, whilst she=E2=80=99s trying to e=
xecute B.J. via firing squad. What=E2=80=99s crazy is not only does she sur=
vive a robot fist to the face, but she=E2=80=99s still willing to get face-=
to-face with B.J. to taunt him, smushed face and all. -&nbsp;<em>Matt Kim</=
em><p></p>
<p><a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/ENGEL=
-FACE-SMASH.png" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/ImageObject"=
><img alt=3D"ENGEL FACE SMASH" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp-image-218=
4191" data-src=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/=
ENGEL-FACE-SMASH-720x405.png" height=3D"405" src=3D"data:image/svg+xml,%3Cs=
vg xmlns=3D'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox=3D'0 0 16 9'%3E%3C/svg%3E" =
width=3D"720" data-position=3D"3"><link href=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/=
wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/ENGEL-FACE-SMASH-720x405.png" itemprop=3D"url=
"></a>
</p><h2>Engel Raids the Resistance HQ in Wolfenstein: The New Order</h2>
Frau Engel doesn=E2=80=99t wait too long to pay B.J. and the resistance bac=
k for the whole smushed face incident, as while B.J. is off stealing nuclea=
r launch codes on the moon, Engel locates the resistance base in Berlin and=
 nearly cripple them by killing or capturing most of B.J.=E2=80=99s friends=
. It was surprising, led to the deaths of major characters like Klaus and T=
ekla, and it perfectly set the stage for the climax of New Order.&nbsp;<em>=
- Mitchell Saltzman</em><p></p>
<p><a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/ENGEL=
RAIDSRESISTANCE-.png" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/ImageOb=
ject"><img alt=3D"ENGELRAIDSRESISTANCE" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp-=
image-2184192" data-src=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com=
/2019/07/ENGELRAIDSRESISTANCE--720x405.png" height=3D"405" src=3D"data:imag=
e/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=3D'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox=3D'0 0 16 9'%=
3E%3C/svg%3E" width=3D"720" data-position=3D"4"><link href=3D"https://oyste=
r.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/ENGELRAIDSRESISTANCE--720x405.p=
ng" itemprop=3D"url"></a>
</p><div class=3D"vplayer"><iframe allow=3D"autoplay" allowautoplay=3D"" al=
lowfullscreen=3D"" class=3D"video" data-src=3D"https://widgets.ign.com/vide=
o/embed/content.html?url=3Dhttps://www.ign.com/videos/2019/07/24/wolfenstei=
n-youngblood-official-launch-trailer" gesture=3D"media" scrolling=3D"no"></=
iframe></div>
<p></p><h2>Engel Kills Caroline Becker in Wolfenstein 2: The New Colossus</=
h2>
For all the gonzo humor present in the rebooted Wolfenstein series, it=E2=
=80=99s also very dark. Wolfenstein 2 might start at one of its darkest poi=
nts when arch-nemesis Frau Engel murders B.J.=E2=80=99s close ally and frie=
nd Caroline Becker. But it=E2=80=99s not a quick death for Becker. Engel fi=
rst tries to force her own daughter to execute the paralyzed Engel before d=
oing the deed herself. And she immediately follows up the gruesome scene by=
 torturing B.J. psychologically with Becker=E2=80=99s death. Executions don=
=E2=80=99t get darker, or crazier than this. -&nbsp;<em>Matt Kim</em><p></p=
>
<p><a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/ENGEL=
KILLSCAROLINE.png" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/ImageObjec=
t"><img alt=3D"ENGELKILLSCAROLINE" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp-image=
-2184193" data-src=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019=
/07/ENGELKILLSCAROLINE-720x405.png" height=3D"405" src=3D"data:image/svg+xm=
l,%3Csvg xmlns=3D'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox=3D'0 0 16 9'%3E%3C/sv=
g%3E" width=3D"720" data-position=3D"5"><link href=3D"https://oyster.ignimg=
s.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/ENGELKILLSCAROLINE-720x405.png" itempro=
p=3D"url"></a>
</p><h2>Anya Goes Rambo in Wolfenstein 2: The New Colossus</h2>
The scene where Anya saves B.J. in The New Colossus is primarily notable be=
cause she did it topless, pregnant, and covered in blood. If there=E2=80=99=
s ever been a more cathartic image than this in a video game, I don=E2=80=
=99t want to know about it.&nbsp;<em> Lucy O'Brien</em><p></p>
<p><a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/ANYAT=
OPLESS.jpg" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/ImageObject"><img=
 alt=3D"ANYATOPLESS" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2184194" data=
-src=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/ANYATOPLES=
S-720x405.jpg" height=3D"405" src=3D"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=3D'htt=
p://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox=3D'0 0 16 9'%3E%3C/svg%3E" width=3D"720" d=
ata-position=3D"6"><link href=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.i=
gn.com/2019/07/ANYATOPLESS-720x405.jpg" itemprop=3D"url"></a>
</p><h2>The Choice to Kill Fergus or Wyatt in Wolfenstein: The New Order</h=
2>
In Wolfenstein: The New Order, antagonist Deathshead asks you to choose whi=
ch one of your comrades, Fergus or Wyatt, he should kill. It=E2=80=99s a ho=
rrific Sophie=E2=80=99s choice, made worse by the incredibly disgusting way=
 in which Deathshead murders whatever poor soul you sacrifice.&nbsp;&nbsp;<=
em>- Lucy O'Brien</em><p></p>
<p><a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/Choic=
e.png" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/ImageObject"><img alt=
=3D"Choice" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2184196" data-src=3D"h=
ttps://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/Choice-720x405.png"=
 height=3D"405" src=3D"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=3D'http://www.w3.org=
/2000/svg' viewBox=3D'0 0 16 9'%3E%3C/svg%3E" width=3D"720" data-position=
=3D"7"><link href=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/=
07/Choice-720x405.png" itemprop=3D"url"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p></p><div class=3D"vplayer"><iframe allow=3D"autoplay" allowautoplay=3D""=
 allowfullscreen=3D"" class=3D"video" data-src=3D"https://widgets.ign.com/v=
ideo/embed/content.html?url=3Dhttps://www.ign.com/videos/2018/06/29/wolfens=
tein-2-the-new-colossus-graphics-comparison-switch-vs-pc" gesture=3D"media"=
 scrolling=3D"no"></iframe></div>
<p></p><h2>What Actually Happens to Fergus or Wyatt in Wolfenstein: The New=
 Order</h2>
<p dir=3D"ltr">...which bring us to what Deathshead actually does. In a sce=
ne that could only be described as =E2=80=98graphic=E2=80=99 in a game so a=
lready soaked in gore, Deathshead drills a hole into Wyatt or Fergus' brain=
 and sucks it out into a tube. Later on in The New Order Deathshead reveals=
 he put the brain into the head of a robot, which eventually tries to kill =
you, and then later begs for the sweet release of death. What a torturous w=
ay to go.&nbsp;<em>- Lucy O'Brien</em>
</p><p dir=3D"ltr">&nbsp;<a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg=
.ign.com/2019/07/WYATTDEATH.png" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/ImageObject"><img alt=3D"WYATTDEATH" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp=
-image-2184197" data-src=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.co=
m/2019/07/WYATTDEATH-720x405.png" height=3D"405" src=3D"data:image/svg+xml,=
%3Csvg xmlns=3D'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox=3D'0 0 16 9'%3E%3C/svg%=
3E" width=3D"720" data-position=3D"8"><link href=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.=
com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/WYATTDEATH-720x405.png" itemprop=3D"url">=
</a>
</p><p></p><h2>Blaskowitz gets Beheaded in Wolfenstein 2: The New Colossus<=
/h2>
B.J. Blazkowicz straight-up died in Wolfenstein The New Colossus, and it wa=
s the best moment in the whole game. For most of the first half of The New =
Colossus, B.J. was in dire straits. Weakened from his fight at the end of W=
olfenstein: The New Order, B.J. spent much of the game on life support. So =
how did he end up recovering in time to liberate America from the Nazis? By=
 getting beheaded in a publicly televised execution, only for his friends t=
o quickly steal B.J.=E2=80=99s decapitated head and surgically attach it to=
 the body of a Nazi super-soldier. Weird flex, but okay.&nbsp;<em>- Matt Ki=
m</em><p></p>
<p><a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/BEHEA=
DING-.png" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/ImageObject"><img =
alt=3D"BEHEADING" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2184198" data-sr=
c=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/BEHEADING--72=
0x405.png" height=3D"405" src=3D"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=3D'http://=
www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox=3D'0 0 16 9'%3E%3C/svg%3E" width=3D"720" data-=
position=3D"9"><link href=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.c=
om/2019/07/BEHEADING--720x405.png" itemprop=3D"url"></a>
</p><h2>Frau Engel Gets What She Deserves</h2>
<p dir=3D"ltr">New Colossus ends without a big final battle against a notab=
le villain, which would be kind of a disappointment, if not for the fact th=
at right after the big final battle, you and your crew interrupt a national=
 late night interview with Frau Engel to deliver her exactly what she deser=
ves, a hatchet through her evil Nazi skull. It=E2=80=99s one of the most gr=
aphic =E2=80=9Choly shit=E2=80=9D moments of the series, but also strangely=
 one of the most feel-good moments as well.&nbsp;<em>- Mitchell Saltzman&nb=
sp;</em>
</p><p dir=3D"ltr"><a href=3D"http://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.c=
om/2019/07/ENGELDEATH.png" itemscope=3D"" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/Im=
ageObject"><img alt=3D"ENGELDEATH" class=3D"aligncenter size-large wp-image=
-2184199" data-src=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/wordpress/stg.ign.com/2019=
/07/ENGELDEATH-720x405.png" height=3D"405" src=3D"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg=
 xmlns=3D'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox=3D'0 0 16 9'%3E%3C/svg%3E" wi=
dth=3D"720" data-position=3D"10"><link href=3D"https://oyster.ignimgs.com/w=
ordpress/stg.ign.com/2019/07/ENGELDEATH-720x405.png" itemprop=3D"url"></a>
For more Wolfenstein Youngblood, make sure to check out our <a href=3D"http=
s://www.ign.com/articles/2019/07/25/wolfenstein-youngblood-review">full rev=
iew</a> or check out the entire story for yourself by <a href=3D"https://ww=
w.ign.com/videos/2019/07/26/wolfenstein-youngblood-the-movie-all-cutscenes"=
>watching all of the cutscenes</a>.</p><p></p>
<p></p><hr>
